       Navigation:



   [personalize_samp2.gif]

   You can change the menu on the left to show Department catagories OR
   County Services topics by clicking "personalize" at the bottom of the
   homepage or by clicking the "View by .." link to the right of the
   menu..

   [how_layers.gif] Clicking one of the menu links, pops up a box in the
   center of the page that has the links to the individual County
   Departments/Services.

   [how_quick.gif] We also provide you with "Quick Links" to ten of our
   most popular web services. These links take you directly to the
   service/application.

   [how_map.gif] If you still can't find what you are looking for, try our
   "Site Map". It has links to virtually every county web page.
       Features:
   [how_search.gif]

   Another way to quickly find information is using our search feature.
   Click here for search tips.

   [how_spotlight.gif] Twice a month we will be spotlighing and linking to
   an online county service in this area of the homepage. We hope this
   will familiarize you with more of the services Maricopa County has to
   offer online..

   [how_news.gif] Our "News" section has a brief of the most recent County
   news/press releases and also provides a link to the full story. Also,
   clicking the word "News" at the top will take you to a page with links
   to other current/past press releases.

   [how_trivia.gif] Here we have a fun "Maricopa Trivia" section.
   Refreshing the page will generate a new Trivia question. Just hover
   over the question to see the answer or click it for a pop-up box.

